<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>新鲜的十二个有趣的笑话。来自俄罗斯的笑话。</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/</link><description>来自俄罗斯的轶事是最有趣的笑话，故事，格言和短语，诗歌，漫画和其他幽默。他们于1995年11月8日发布。由Dima Werner编译</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>轶事＃1 17 Martha 2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-17/#1513595</link><description>- 在每个月结束时，我严格按照诫命生活。&lt;br /&gt; - 正如我所理解的，在本月初，事情发生了巨大变化吗？&lt;br /&gt; - 是的，卡上的薪水出现在我身上。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-17/#1513595</guid></item><item><title>轶事＃2 17 Martha 2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-17/#1513596</link><description>我很高兴代表们开始使用AI。尽管如此，这还是智力。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-17/#1513596</guid></item><item><title>轶事＃3 for 17 Martha 2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-17/#1513597</link><description>根据国际奥委会和托马斯·巴赫（Thomas Bach）的说法，俄罗斯人扔了一个阿尔及利亚拳击手的成员。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-17/#1513597</guid></item><item><title>轶事＃4 for 17 Martha 2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-17/#1513598</link><description>如果妻子疯了，那是因为您值得更多！</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-17/#1513598</guid></item><item><title>轶事＃5 17 Martha 2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-17/#1513599</link><description>备受喜爱的浴室必须完全洗。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-17/#1513599</guid></item><item><title>anecdot＃6 for 17 Martha 2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-17/#1513600</link><description>难怪他们说：“麻烦并不孤单。”&lt;br /&gt;他不仅在电梯里废plo乱，而且还陷入了它...</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-17/#1513600</guid></item><item><title>轶事7玛莎2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-17/#1513601</link><description>我非常了解地理，以至于我可以从记忆中绘制科罗拉多州状态的地图！</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-17/#1513601</guid></item><item><title>17 Martha 2025的Anecdot＃8</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-17/#1513602</link><description>特种部队。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-17/#1513602</guid></item><item><title>轶事9玛莎2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-17/#1513603</link><description>在法国，他们要求美国返回自由女神像。显然，它在法国的自由是一个大问题。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-17/#1513603</guid></item><item><title>17 Martha 2025的Anecdot＃10</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-17/#1513604</link><description>有说服的朋友的学士学位：&lt;br /&gt; - 为什么我需要这个家庭？我一个人住，我吃我想要的东西，我想要的时候放松，没人看到！&lt;br /&gt;突然从厨房听到了声音：&lt;br /&gt; - 在炉子上的Borsch冷却，您会温暖自己还是我来？&lt;br /&gt;他紧张地拉直领带：&lt;br /&gt; - 好吧，妈妈与众不同...</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-17/#1513604</guid></item></channel></rss>